          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The Copy and Fax Room smells like hot plastic and old staples.\n\nThe fax machine sits under a laminated sign that says: \u201cTRANSMISSIONS ARE RECORDS.\u201d\n\nIn your hands: the training waiver template you pulled earlier\u2014blank where it matters.",
