        },
        {
          "id": "N021_SEND_NARR",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The machine takes the first page like it\u2019s accepting blame.\n\nIt dials. It squeals. It goes quiet in a way that suggests \u201cquiet\u201d is also a setting with liability implications.",
          "next": "N022_SEND_NARR2"
        },
        {
          "id": "N022_SEND_NARR2",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "A minute later, the tray twitches.",
          "next": "N100_RETURN_INTRO"
        },
        {
          "id": "N030_TEMPLATE_READ",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The template is written in a tone that assumes someone will later ask why it existed.\n\nThe checkbox reads: \u201cI acknowledge receipt of required training materials.\u201d\n\nNot \u201cI completed.\u201d Not \u201cI understood.\u201d\n\nJust receipt\u2014like training is a package that can be delivered to a body.",
          "next": "N031_AFTER_TEMPLATE_MENU"
        },
        {
